items.jobDescribe:
University of Nottingham Ningbo China is seeking to recruit a HR Officer or HR Assistant

Your Responsibility
Your key responsibilities include:
1. Lead the team to provide professional advice and services on staff compensation and benefits related matters;
2. Support team members and ensure high standard and quality of work as well as high accuracy and efficiency; Responsible for staff benefits operations assigned by line manager; 
3. Manage employee exit process and conduct exit interview with leaving staff when necessary; 
4. Take HR responsibility for the full cycle of recruitment process and talent pool management; 
5. Maintain recruitment and employment records and conduct data analysis and prepare recruitment and employment reports regularly for manager to review;
6. Conduct market research and identify engagement focus areas to plan engagement projects/activities;
7. Develop, organize and promote staff engagement projects/activities to increase internal communications and enrich engaging culture;
8. Support manager to deliver projects and lead projects when asked. Support the implementation of projects led by other HR teams when needed.


About You
1. Bachelor’s degree in HR, Business, Marketing, Communication, English or other related discipline
2. Excellent analytical skills and relationship-building skills 
3. Excellent planning and time management skills
4. Excellent communication and responsive skills - verbal, written and presentation in English
5. Proficient computer skills (e.g. Microsoft Office) 
6. Good collaboration and coordination skills
7. Relevant HR experience
8. Project management and change management experience

1.熟练使用办公软件，有一定的写作水平和较强的语言表达能力、计划与执行能力、人际沟通能力;
2.熟悉国家人力资源相关法律法规、劳动合同法等知识;
3.负责考勤管理、年假管理与统计;
4.负责员工社保招工退工、公积金转入转出;
5.了解居住证积分申请流程、居转户办理流程、员工工伤办理流程等人事专项工作;
6.搭建人事各类管理制度、绩效方案的调整、员工培训等。
[工作内容]
1、负责简历筛选、招聘需求的更新及职位发布；
2、负责收集、分析简历和分类简历，建立系统的人才库；
3、负责电话面试和初步面试，对职位候选者做初步把控；
4、负责组织、协调各种招聘活动，规范招聘流程并独立完成招聘任务
5、负责人力资源信息系统及各类人事档案的管理;
6、每月及时准确的完成社保及公积金的缴纳;
7、负责公司员工考勤的核实任务，与财务对接员工薪酬相关事宜;
8、组织做好企业人事制度的培训工作，协助上级执行人力资源规划;
完成领导安排及临时交办或需配合其他部门的各项工作
